      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Rotten Fruit",
        "Client": "Innocent Felyne",
        "Description": "It was my fur-st time seeing a Bishaten\r\nup close. It looked so playful and fur-\r\niendly! It even started throwing fruit to\r\nme. I thought they were purr-esents\r\nbut one of them blinded me with a flash\r\nand the other zapped my tail! What\r\na meanie! Go teach it a lesson fur me!",
        "Target": "Hunt a Bishaten",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Fruit putride",
        "Client": "Felyne innocent",
        "Description": "C\u0027\u00E9tait la premi\u00E8re fois que je\r\nvoyais un Bishaten de si pr\u00E8s. Il\r\ns\u0027est mis \u00E0 me jeter des fruits,\r\net j\u0027ai cru qu\u0027il m\u0027offrait des\r\ncadeaux, mais c\u0027\u00E9taient des bombes !\r\nVa lui donner une le\u00E7on, chat lui\r\napprendra les bonnes mani\u00E8res !",
        "Target": "Chasser un Bishaten",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Frutto marcio",
        "Client": "Felyne innocente",
        "Description": "Non avevo mai visto un\r\nBishaten cos\u00EC da vicino. Ha\r\niniziato a lanciarmi dei frutti\r\naddosso. Pensavo fossero\r\nregali, miao uno mi ha accecato\r\ne l\u0027altro mi ha colpito la coda.\r\nCattivone! Dagli una lezione!",
        "Target": "Caccia un Bishaten",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Verdorbene Fr\u00FCchte",
        "Client": "Unschuldiger Felyne",
        "Description": "Ich war zum ersten Mal einem Bishaten\r\nganz nah. Er sah so verspielt und lieb\r\naus! Er hat mir sogar Fr\u00FCchte zugeworfen.\r\nGeschenke, dachte ich, aber eine hat\r\nmich mit einem Blitz geblendet, eine\r\nandere meinen Schwanz geschockt! So\r\nein Fiesling! Bring ihm Manieren bei!",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Bishaten.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Fruta podrida",
        "Client": "Felyne inocente",
        "Description": "Pens\u00E9 que, cuando un Bishaten\r\nme empez\u00F3 a tirar fruta, se\r\ntrataba de un regalo, \u00A1pero\r\ndaban calambre! Fue terrible,\r\ny estoy seguro de que lo hizo\r\nadrede. \u00BFPodr\u00EDas darle una\r\nlecci\u00F3n, por favor?",
        "Target": "Caza un Bishaten",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
